[SkillPath "competitive_bidding/dont"]
[Student "S"]
{This is a perfect hand with which to Disturb the Opponent's No Trump. You double and partner bids 2\C, the relay bid.

What do you say next? 

You say pass, of course.}

[Event ""]
[Site ""]
[Date ""]
[Board "2"]
[Dealer "N"]
[Vulnerable "NS"]
[Deal "N:JT2.AJ87.AK.AT64 KQ985.64.86.KQ92 43.K92.QT953.J73 A76.QT53.J742.85"]
[Declarer "E"]
[Contract "2S"]
[Result ""]
[Auction "N"]
1NT 2C pass 2D pass 2S pass pass pass
[BCFlags "1f"]
[RotationNote "Board 2, chOption: E, chBasis: N, basisKind:Declarer, nOption:1, nBasis: 0, nRot: 1, useStandardVul: true"]
[VersionToken "7326f14cc986597a418ff84eb09bc30b446d8a6e395feec1a980299949440880"]
[Category "Competitive Bidding"]
[Difficulty "intermediate"]
[SkillPath "competitive_bidding/dont"]
[Student "S"]
{Partner has two suits, \Cs and something else.

With \Cs your worst suit, you prefer to play in something else. So you bid the next suit up-the-line, which is 2\D.

Partner corrects to 2\S, his "something else" and you pass.}

[Event ""]
[Site ""]
[Date ""]
[Board "3"]
[Dealer "E"]
[Vulnerable "EW"]
[Deal "E:QJ5.A5.AJT74.A62 87.KQJT87.965.83 T94.632.KQ32.JT4 AK632.94.8.KQ975"]
[Declarer "S"]
