[VersionToken "b209ed09999ba0f472eb03ea8b50ad8f803c81a6d8c84abfc354c102a3199054"]
[Category "Competitive Bidding"]
[Difficulty "intermediate"]
[SkillPath "competitive_bidding/dont"]
[Student "S"]
{You have 12 HCP, certainly enough to use DONT in either seat. With your black 2-suiter you bid the lowest one, 2\C.

Partner says 2\H.  

Partner would have bid 2\D, the next suit up the line, to ask you to name your other suit. His 2\H bid says he wants to play right there.

So you pass.}

