[SkillPath "competitive_bidding/dont"]
[Student "S"]
{With 16 points and a balanced hand you were planning on opening 1NT yourself.

But one of the consequences of playing DONT is that you have no bid to describe this hand. You cannot double because then partner would just bid 2\C as a relay and you wouldn't know where to go.

So you pass.}

